<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<!-- HERO -->
<header class="about-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><span>About</span></div>
    <h1>Coastal Karnataka's<br>most trusted<br><span class="it">property team.</span></h1>
    <p>For over 15 years, families across Udupi, Mangaluru, Manipal and the Western Ghats have trusted us to find the right home, negotiate the right price and close the right way. One team. No middlemen. No surprises.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div><div class="v">15+</div><div class="l">Years in the market</div></div>
      <div><div class="v">₹500Cr+</div><div class="l">Transacted</div></div>
      <div><div class="v">1,200+</div><div class="l">Happy families</div></div>
      <div><div class="v">4.9 ★</div><div class="l">Client rating</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- TRUST SCORE BAND -->
<section class="rating-band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="r-score">4.9</div>
    <div class="r-stars">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="#C2A05A"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="#C2A05A"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="#C2A05A"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="#C2A05A"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="#C2A05A"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="r-label">Average rating · 1,200+ verified clients</div>
    <div class="r-note">Across Udupi, Mangaluru, Manipal and the Western Ghats</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO WE ARE -->
<section class="about-sec">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="prose reveal">
        <span class="label">Who we are</span>
        <h2>Built on the coast.<br><span class="it">Rooted in trust.</span></h2>
        <p>RichManAssets was founded in Mangaluru in 2009, when the coastal Karnataka property market was fragmented, opaque and difficult to navigate for buyers and sellers alike. We built one team to fix that.</p>
        <p>Today we are one of the most recognised property consultancies across the Udupi–Mangaluru coastal corridor, covering residential sales, commercial leasing, plot transactions, home finance and legal services from a single desk.</p>
        <p>We are powered by <strong>Vittu Bharat Associates LLP</strong>, with a legal desk empaneled with SBI, HDFC, Karnataka Bank and 8 other national lenders.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="media-col dark reveal">
        <h3>One desk for<br><span class="it">everything</span> property.</h3>
        <p>Most property journeys in coastal Karnataka involve a broker who doesn't do loans, a banker who doesn't understand title, and a lawyer who gets called too late. We put all three roles in-house so nothing falls through the cracks.</p>
        <div class="trust-block" style="background:rgba(247,244,237,.06);border-radius:10px;padding:20px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-top:8px">
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px">
            <div style="font-family:var(--f-display);font-size:30px;font-weight:500;color:var(--gold)">11</div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(247,244,237,.44)">Banking partners</div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px">
            <div style="font-family:var(--f-display);font-size:30px;font-weight:500;color:var(--gold)">100%</div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(247,244,237,.44)">Title-clear listings</div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px">
            <div style="font-family:var(--f-display);font-size:30px;font-weight:500;color:var(--gold)">8</div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(247,244,237,.44)">Service lines</div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px">
            <div style="font-family:var(--f-display);font-size:30px;font-weight:500;color:var(--gold)">1 day</div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(247,244,237,.44)">Typical response time</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- UDUPI REGION SEO FOCUS -->
<section class="about-sec" style="background:var(--paper-2);padding:clamp(64px,9vw,112px) 0">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="prose" style="max-width:70ch;margin-bottom:clamp(32px,4vw,52px)">
      <span class="label">Where we operate</span>
      <h2>The property specialists<br>for <span class="it">Udupi District</span> and beyond.</h2>
      <p>The Udupi and Dakshina Kannada coastal strip is one of South India's most desirable property markets, driven by a combination of natural beauty, strong NRI investment, university demand from Manipal and growing retirement interest from metros. We know every pocket of this coastline.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="loc-grid">
      <div class="loc-card reveal">
        <h4>Udupi</h4>
        <p>Temple city with strong rental demand driven by Manipal University, hospitals and tourism. Excellent infrastructure, reliable connectivity.</p>
        <div class="pill-row"><span class="pill">Residential</span><span class="pill">Plots</span><span class="pill">Commercial</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loc-card reveal">
        <h4>Manipal</h4>
        <p>Planned plateau university town with India's largest private medical school. Perpetual rental demand from students, faculty and international researchers.</p>
        <div class="pill-row"><span class="pill">Houses</span><span class="pill">Investment</span><span class="pill">Rentals</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loc-card reveal">
        <h4>Mangaluru</h4>
        <p>Karnataka's second-largest city. Port, airport, banking hub. Strong commercial and residential market with consistent NRI buyer interest from Gulf, UK and US.</p>
        <div class="pill-row"><span class="pill">Commercial</span><span class="pill">Apartments</span><span class="pill">Villas</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loc-card reveal">
        <h4>Surathkal</h4>
        <p>NITK campus zone. High-demand rental corridor. Beachfront properties attract both lifestyle buyers and investors seeking consistent occupancy.</p>
        <div class="pill-row"><span class="pill">Beach villas</span><span class="pill">Rentals</span><span class="pill">Plots</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loc-card reveal">
        <h4>Kundapur</h4>
        <p>Fast-growing coastal town between Udupi and Mangaluru. Agricultural and residential land at significantly lower entry prices than city corridors.</p>
        <div class="pill-row"><span class="pill">Plots</span><span class="pill">Agri land</span><span class="pill">Houses</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loc-card reveal">
        <h4>Maravanthe & Kapu</h4>
        <p>The most scenic stretch of NH-66, with sea on one side and backwater on the other. Increasingly sought by second-home buyers from Bangalore and Mumbai.</p>
        <div class="pill-row"><span class="pill">Beach sites</span><span class="pill">Villas</span><span class="pill">Plots</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loc-card reveal">
        <h4>Sakleshpur</h4>
        <p>Cool, misty hill station in Hassan district. Coffee and areca estate country. Rising demand from Bangalore buyers looking for working estates and retreats.</p>
        <div class="pill-row"><span class="pill">Estates</span><span class="pill">Agri</span><span class="pill">Hill homes</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loc-card reveal">
        <h4>Chikmagalur</h4>
        <p>Karnataka's original coffee country at 1,000m elevation. Plantation estates, resort properties and hill bungalows within 5 hours of Bangalore.</p>
        <div class="pill-row"><span class="pill">Coffee estates</span><span class="pill">Retreats</span><span class="pill">Plots</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY WE'RE DIFFERENT -->
<section class="about-sec">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="prose" style="max-width:60ch;margin-bottom:clamp(28px,3.6vw,48px)">
      <span class="label">Our promise</span>
      <h2>What makes us<br><span class="it">different.</span></h2>
      <p>Most agencies are transaction-focused. We are relationship-focused, which is why over 60% of our business comes from referrals and repeat clients.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <span class="n">01</span>
        <h4>Title-clear only</h4>
        <p>We refuse to list a property until our in-house legal desk has verified the title, checked for encumbrances and confirmed clean ownership. No exceptions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <span class="n">02</span>
        <h4>Honest pricing</h4>
        <p>We tell you the realistic market rate, not the aspirational one. We have walked away from listings where the seller's price was simply not justifiable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <span class="n">03</span>
        <h4>One team, no handoffs</h4>
        <p>Your single point of contact handles everything: property, loan, legal, interiors. You are never passed from department to department.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <span class="n">04</span>
        <h4>Banking empanelment</h4>
        <p>Our advocate is empaneled with SBI, HDFC, Karnataka Bank and 8 other lenders, which means faster loan sanctions and better rates than going to a bank cold.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <span class="n">05</span>
        <h4>NRI specialist desk</h4>
        <p>We have handled hundreds of NRI transactions across the UK, US and Gulf countries. Power of attorney, FEMA compliance and repatriation paperwork handled completely.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <span class="n">06</span>
        <h4>Post-sale management</h4>
        <p>We stay involved after the keys change hands, handling tenant management, maintenance and property protection for clients who live away from their investment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
<section class="about-sec" style="background:var(--paper-2);padding:clamp(64px,9vw,112px) 0">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="intro-head" style="margin-bottom:clamp(32px,4vw,52px)">
      <h2 class="fx">Clients speak for <span class="it">themselves.</span></h2>
      <p class="sub fx">Real words from families and investors along the coastal Karnataka corridor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tcards">
      <% testimonials.forEach(function(t) { %>
      <div class="tcard reveal">
        <div class="stars">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 1l2 4.2 4.6.6-3.4 3.2.9 4.6L8 11.4 3.9 13.6l.9-4.6L1.4 5.8 6 5.2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote>"<%= t.quote %>"</blockquote>
        <div class="who"><span class="av"><%= t.initials %></span><div><b><%= t.name %></b><span><%= t.role %></span></div></div>
      </div>
      <% }) %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ (visible content backing FAQ schema) -->
<section class="sec intro" id="faq" data-screen-label="FAQ">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:820px">
    <div class="intro-head" style="margin-bottom:8px">
      <h2 class="fx">Frequently asked <span class="it">questions.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary>Which areas do you cover for property in coastal Karnataka?</summary>
        <p>We cover Udupi, Mangaluru, Manipal, Surathkal, Mulki, Kapu, Padubidri, Maravanthe and the wider Dakshina Kannada and Udupi districts, plus hill stations like Sakleshpur and Chikmagalur.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you help with home loans and legal paperwork?</summary>
        <p>Yes. We have direct tie-ups with SBI, Bank of Baroda, HDFC, Karnataka Bank and others for fast, pre-approved home and project loans, and an in-house advocate for title checks, due diligence and registration.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Are your property listings title-verified?</summary>
        <p>Every listing is title-checked and verified before we publish it. We only market title-clear property across Udupi and Mangaluru.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you work with NRI buyers and investors?</summary>
        <p>Yes. We offer end-to-end NRI services including remote site visits, documentation, loans, registration and full property management after purchase.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="lead">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="lead-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center;place-items:center">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker" style="color:var(--gold)"><span class="gold-line"></span>Ready to talk?</span>
      <h2 style="margin-top:14px">Find your place on the <span class="it">Karnataka coast.</span></h2>
      <p class="lead-sub" style="margin-inline:auto;margin-top:12px">One conversation with a specialist is all it takes to get started, whether buying, selling, renting or investing.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-top:24px">
        <a class="btn btn-dark" href="/properties"><span>Browse properties</span><span class="arr">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact"><span>Talk to us</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div></div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<script>
  const nav = document.getElementById('nav');
  nav.classList.add('solid');
  const io = new IntersectionObserver((es) => es.forEach(e => {
    if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('in'); io.unobserve(e.target); }
  }), { threshold: .08, rootMargin: '0px 0px -4% 0px' });
  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => io.observe(el));
</script>
</body>
</html>
